com.infinityrefactoring.reflections

Class DelegatedInstanceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.infinityrefactoring.reflections.DelegatedInstanceFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstanceFactory

    public class DelegatedInstanceFactory
extends Object
implements InstanceFactory
    This instance factory delegate the building process to a specific factory, if exists a factory for the given class, otherwise uses the default constructor.
